  "commentary": "**DEALER HEDGING COMMENTARY:**\n\nWith SPX at 6565.78 sitting just above the GEX flip at 6561 in PIN regime, dealers are currently in stabilizing mode and likely selling gamma into this move higher, creating natural resistance as we approach the massive 6580 wall (+23.4B GEX). The thick positive gamma structure from 6565-6600 should act as a magnet, dampening volatility and encouraging mean reversion within this range. Watch 6561 as the critical flip level - any break below turns dealers from stabilizers to accelerators, while the 6580 level becomes the key resistance where dealer selling pressure intensifies significantly.",
